title: Eps. 161 - Last Guys Finish Last
description:
In 2019 ET is on a quest to study what it takes to really be able to execute at a high level. On today’s podcast, he brings a case study involving effort -vs- execution. A lot of people think that they’re effort is enough to get them to the next level. Specifically good people who try hard but just aren’t performing at a level they need to perform at. ET and the squad explain to us why effort is sometimes rewarded but execution is worshipped.
